    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The covering, usually wood boards, plywood, or wallboard, placed over the exterior studding or rafters of a building; provides a base for the application of wall or roof siding.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
